    <div xml:id="PN255-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. <gap quantity="6" reason="lost" unit="character"/>vaṉparaṇar pāṭiyatu.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="PN255">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>aiyō veṉiṉyāṉ puliyañ cuvalē</l>
<l>yaṇaittaṉaṉ koḷiṉē yakaṉmār peṭukkavallē</l>
<l>ṉeṉpōṟ peruvitirp puṟuka niṉṉai</l>
<l>yiṉṉā tuṟṟa vaṟaṉil kūṟṟē</l>
<l>niraivaḷai muṉkai paṟṟi</l>
<l>varainiḻaṟ cērka naṭatticiṟ ciṟitē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l corresp="1">  If [you] say “aiyō”, I am afraid of the tiger. </l>
<l corresp="2">If I take [him] as one who touches, I won’t be able to rouse [him] with wide chest. </l>
<l corresp="4a-c">May you experience a great tremble like me, </l>
<l corresp="5">virtuless Death who experienced something displeasing for you. </l>
<l corresp="5">Gripping the forearm with bangles in a row </l>
<l corresp="6">we shall join the shade of the mountain; let us walk a little. </l>
</lg>
    </div>
